cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.NE 

The paper proposes a methodology for automatic data annotation using deep learning and Bayesian inference. This falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and computer vision (cs.CV), as well as artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and natural language processing (cs.CL) if the datasets used involve text. The use of neural network architectures also suggests the category of neural networks (cs.NE).
